en:
Been thinkin' recently...
Cornucopia really needs a restaurant!

Was wonderin' if it'd be possible to renovate
this lil' shop here and turn it into somethin'
like that...

I wanted to do somethin' that might benefit
my daughter <c=mocha>Mocha</c> in some way as well.

Could make for nice chemistry between the
places...

Might go and make a start by sellin' drinks...
Ya got any preferences, spectrum?
